?? [ ''Ode to Joy'': Rock Version ]

1587
01:25:25.090 --> 01:25:29.824
Look at me! Hey! Walter!

1588
01:25:29.928 --> 01:25:32.013
A big smile!

1589
01:25:35.928 --> 01:25:39.384
Hold it! Hold it there!
One more! Ready?

1590
01:25:41.225 --> 01:25:44.681
Hold it! Way to go!
Thank you. I got it.

1591
01:25:58.617 --> 01:26:02.691
lt's a very nice house.
and the price is reasonable.

1592
01:26:02.795 --> 01:26:06.068
[ Laughs ] Reasonable? lt's a steal.

1593
01:26:06.172 --> 01:26:09.241
Oh. honey!
lt's so beautiful.

1594
01:26:09.345 --> 01:26:11.201
You buy or not?

1595
01:26:11.306 --> 01:26:13.200
We're buying.
- [ Giggles ]

1596
01:26:13.305 --> 01:26:16.995
You can count it if you like.
but you'll find it's all there.

1597
01:26:17.099 --> 01:26:18.998
[ Woman ] Carlos. come on!

1598
01:26:19.102 --> 01:26:22.679
We haven't got all day!
Let's go!

1599
